		<script>
		function getFilterStatus(filterSender)
		{
			//alert(event.target.id);
			document.getElementById("overlay").style.display  = "block";
			//document.getElementById(filterSender).checked = true;
			if(filterSender == 'board'){
				//set the ddl list to nothing
				document.getElementById('boardCode').value = '';
			}
			if(filterSender == 'licType'){
				//set the ddl list to nothing
				document.getElementById('licenseType').value = '';
			}
			document.getElementById("mainForm").submit();
		}
		function removeCheck(theOneToUncheck)
		{
			document.getElementById("overlay").style.display  = "block";
			document.getElementById(theOneToUncheck).checked = false;
			document.getElementById("mainForm").submit();			
		}
		</script>

		<script>
					
			
			function filterExpand(filterExpanded){
			
			var fl ="";
			
			switch(filterExpanded)
			{
				case "cityMore":
					fl = "city";
					break;
				case "countyMore":				
					fl = "county";					
					break;
				case "clientCodeMore":				
					fl = "clientCode";					
					break;
				case "boardCodeMore":				
					fl = "boardCode";					
					break;
				case "statusMore":				
					fl = "status";					
					break;
				case "secStatusMore":				
					fl = "secStatus";					
					break;
				case "licSecStatMore":				
					fl = "licSecStat";					
					break;
				default:
					fl = "";
					break;	
			}
			
				if(document.getElementById( fl+"More").innerHTML =="(+ More)")
				{			
					document.getElementById(fl+"More").innerHTML = "(- Less)";
					var x = $('#'+fl+'FL').height();
					
					if (x >= '450'){
					document.getElementById(fl+'Container').style.height = "450px"
					}else{document.getElementById(fl+'Container').style.height = x + "px";}
				}
				else{
					document.getElementById(fl+"More").innerHTML = "(+ More)";
					document.getElementById(fl+'Container').style.height = "150px"
				}
				
			}
			
			
			function filterClear(filterCleared) 
			{
				//srchSubmitHomeMobile
			
				document.getElementById("overlay").style.display  = "block";
			
				var flc ="";
			
				switch(filterCleared)
				{
					case "cityClear":
						flc = "city";
						break;
					case "countyClear":				
						flc = "cnty";					
						break;
					case "clientCode":				
						flc = "clientCode";					
						break;
					case "boardCode":				
						flc = "boardCode";					
						break;
					case "statusClear":				
						flc = "status";					
						break;
					case "secStatusClear":				
						flc = "secStatus";					
						break;
					case "licSecStatMore":				
						flc = "licSecStat";					
						break;
					case "srchSubmitHomeMobile":	
						document.getElementById('boardCode').value = document.getElementById('boardCodeM').value;
						document.getElementById('licenseType').value = document.getElementById('licenseTypeM').value;
						document.getElementById('licenseNumber').value = document.getElementById('licenseNumberM').value; 
						document.getElementById('busName').value = document.getElementById('busNameM').value; 
						document.getElementById('firstName').value = document.getElementById('firstNameM').value; 
						document.getElementById('lastName').value = document.getElementById('lastNameM').value; 
						$("#pzip").remove();
						$("#pcnty").remove();
						$("#tzip").remove();
						$("#tcnty").remove();
						$("#retired").remove();
						$("#medActivities").remove();
						$("#currentTrainingStatus").remove();
						$("#primaryPracticeArea").remove();
						$("#secondaryPracticeArea").remove();
						$("#boardCertification").remove();
						$("#postgraduateTrainingYears").remove();
						$("#culturalBackground").remove();
						$("#foreignLanguage").remove();
						//document.getElementById("mainForm").submit();					
						break;
					case "srchSubmit":	
						$("#pzip").remove();
						$("#pcnty").remove();
						$("#tzip").remove();
						$("#tcnty").remove();
						$("#retired").remove();
						$("#medActivities").remove();
						$("#currentTrainingStatus").remove();
						$("#primaryPracticeArea").remove();
						$("#secondaryPracticeArea").remove();
						$("#boardCertification").remove();
						$("#postgraduateTrainingYears").remove();
						$("#culturalBackground").remove();
						$("#foreignLanguage").remove();
						//document.getElementById("mainForm").submit();					
						break;
					default:
						flc = "";
						break;	
				}
				
				var elementsCity = document.querySelectorAll('input[id^="chk_'+flc+'"]');	

				for(var i = 0; i < elementsCity.length; i++) 
				{
				
					if(elementsCity[i].checked)
					{
						elementsCity[i].checked = false;
					}
				}
				document.getElementById("mainForm").submit();	

			}
			function clearForm()
			{
				var elementsCity = document.querySelectorAll('input[id^="chk_"]');	

				for(var i = 0; i < elementsCity.length; i++) 
				{
				
					if(elementsCity[i].checked)
					{
						elementsCity[i].checked = false;
					}
				}
				
				document.getElementById('boardCode').selectedIndex  = "";
				changeTheBoard();
				document.getElementById('licenseType').selectedIndex  = "";
				document.getElementById('licenseNumber').value = ''; 
				document.getElementById('busName').value = ''; 
				document.getElementById('firstName').value = ''; 
				document.getElementById('lastName').value = ''; 
			}
			</script>
		</form>
	</body>
			<script type="text/javascript">
		    //initialize the 3 popup css class names - create more if needed
		    var matchClass = ['popup1', 'popup2', 'popup3', 'newTab'];
		    //Set your 3 basic sizes and other options for the class names above - create more if needed
		    var popup1 = 'width=400,height=300,toolbar=0,menubar=0,location=0,status=1,scrollbars=1,resizable=1,left=20,top=20';
		    var popup2 = 'width=800,height=600,toolbar=0,menubar=0,location=0,status=1,scrollbars=1,resizable=1,left=20,top=20';
		    var popup3 = 'width=1000,height=750,toolbar=0,menubar=0,location=0,status=1,scrollbars=1,resizable=1,left=20,top=20';
		    var newTab = '';
		
		  //The pop-up function
		    function tfpop() {
		        var x = 0;
		        var popClass;
		        while (x < matchClass.length) {
		            popClass = "'." + matchClass[x] + "'";
		            $(eval(popClass)).click(function () {
		                if (popClass.indexOf('newTab') == -1) {
		                    var popurl = $(this).attr('href');
		                    var popupSpecs = $(this).attr('class');
		                    var popupName = Math.floor(Math.random() * 10000001);
		                    newwindow = window.open(popurl, popupName, eval(popupSpecs));
		                }
		                else {
		                    $(this).target = "_blank";
		                    window.open($(this).prop('href'))
		                }
		                return false;
		            });
		            x++;
		        }
		    }
		  
		    //Wait until the page loads to call the function
		    $(function () {
		        tfpop();
		    });
		</script>
		
		<script>
		//Make sure the user has scrolled at least double the height of the browser
		var toggleHeight = $(window).outerHeight() * 2;

		$(window).scroll(function() {
			if ($(window).scrollTop() > toggleHeight) {
				//Adds active class to make button visible
				$(".m-backtotop").addClass("active");
				
				//Just some cool text changes
				$('h1 span').text('TA-DA! Now hover it and hit dat!')
				
			} else {
				//Removes active class to make button visible
				$(".m-backtotop").removeClass("active");
				
				//Just some cool text changes
				$('h1 span').text('(start scrolling)')
			}
		});


		//Scrolls the user to the top of the page again
		$(".m-backtotop").click(function() {
			$("html, body").animate({ scrollTop: 0 }, "slow");
			return false;
		});
		</script>
		
<script>
function changeTheBoard(){
		//var arr1 = $('#filterActivity option:not(:selected)');
		//$("#filterSubActivity").children("optgroup[label='" + arr1[j].value + "']").hide();
		//alert('bob')
		$("#licenseType").val([]);
		$("select[name='licenseType'] :selected").removeAttr("selected");

		// using text value to match second select option groups could just as easily be based on value then label text
		var arr = $("select[name='boardCode'] :selected").text();

		if (arr !== '') { // arbitrary value to show all 
		$("select[name='licenseType']").children("optgroup").hide();
		$("select[name='licenseType']").children("optgroup[label='" + arr + "']").show();
		} else {
		$("select[name='licenseType']").children("optgroup").show();
		}
		
	}
    </script>
    <script>
		function changeTheBoardMobile(){
		//var arr1 = $('#filterActivity option:not(:selected)');
		//$("#filterSubActivity").children("optgroup[label='" + arr1[j].value + "']").hide();
		//alert('bob')
		$("#licenseTypeM").val([]);
		$("select[name='licenseTypeM'] :selected").removeAttr("selected");

		// using text value to match second select option groups could just as easily be based on value then label text
		var arr = $("select[name='boardCodeM'] :selected").text();

		if (arr !== '') { // arbitrary value to show all 
		$("select[name='licenseTypeM']").children("optgroup").hide();
		$("select[name='licenseTypeM']").children("optgroup[label='" + arr + "']").show();
		} else {
		$("select[name='licenseTypeM']").children("optgroup").show();
		}
		
	}
    </script>
</html>
